#. Tag: title
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing a Blog Post or a Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid "To delete a blog post from your blog, run the <command>blaze-remove</command> command followed by an appropriate identification number:"
